Package org.glassfish.jersey.client.oauth2

Jersey OAuth 2 Client API.

See:
          Description

Interface Summary
OAuth2CodeGrantFlow The interface that defines OAuth 2 Authorization Code Grant Flow.
OAuth2CodeGrantFlow.Builder<T extends OAuth2CodeGrantFlow.Builder> The builder of OAuth2CodeGrantFlow.
 

Class Summary
ClientIdentifier Client Identifier that contains information about client id and client secret issues by a Service Provider for application.
OAuth2ClientSupport Main class to build the Authorization Flow instances and client filter feature that can supports performing of authenticated OAuth requests.
OAuth2FlowGoogleBuilder Class that provides methods to build OAuth2CodeGrantFlow pre-configured for usage with Google provider.
OAuth2Parameters Class that contains definition od parameters used in OAuth2.
TokenResult Class that contains a result of the Authorization Flow including a access token.
 

Enum Summary
OAuth2CodeGrantFlow.Phase Phase of the Authorization Code Grant Flow.
OAuth2FlowGoogleBuilder.AccessType Enum that defines values for "access_type" parameter used in Google OAuth flow.
OAuth2FlowGoogleBuilder.Display Enum that defines values for "display" parameter used in Google OAuth flow.
OAuth2FlowGoogleBuilder.Prompt Enum that defines values for "prompt" parameter used in Google OAuth flow.
OAuth2Parameters.GrantType Parameter grant_type used in the access token request.
 

Package org.glassfish.jersey.client.oauth2 Description

Jersey OAuth 2 Client API. The API is currently in the state of a BETA version.
